                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p>Have you already mastered standard push-ups and are looking for a more challenging variation? Try deficit push-ups!</p><p>They are an excellent exercise for shoulder, triceps, and chest development. The deeper stretch in the chest and shoulders can also improve your mobility in the upper body.</p><p>This guide will give you all the details you need about deficit push-ups. We cover the benefits, how to incorporate it into your routine, and which muscles they target.</p>                    </div>
